  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要做一个甘特图来展示项目进度。整体分成两个主要阶段，第一部分从2014年初开始，第二部分紧随其后。时间格式就用标准的年月日吧。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "gantt",
        "dateFormat",
        "section"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，我先用YYYY-MM-DD格式设置时间基准。两个section您打算怎么命名？还有第一个任务的具体起止时间能确认一下吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "dateFormat YYYY-MM-DD",
        "section",
        "task"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "第一个section就叫\"Section\"吧，里面放两个任务：A task从1月1号开始持续30天，然后Another task要等A task做完之后再开始，跑20天。第二个section叫\"Another\"，里面再放两个任务。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "section Section",
        "A task",
        "Another task",
        "after a1",
        "30d",
        "20d"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，第一个section已经画好了，A task标记为a1，Another task设置了依赖关系。现在第二个section的\"Another\"里，那两个任务的时间和依赖关系是怎样的？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "section Another",
        "a1",
        "after a1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "第二个section里，Task in sec从1月12号开始，持续12天。最后一个任务another task要等它完成后再开始，需要24天。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Task in sec",
        "2014-01-12",
        "12d",
        "another task",
        "24d"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下：another task是接在Task in sec之后，而不是接在整个项目最后对吧？另外这个任务ID需要我自动生成吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "another task",
        "Task in sec",
        "24d"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，another task紧跟Task in sec，ID你自动处理就行。整个图的标题就叫\"A Gantt Diagram\"吧。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title",
        "A Gantt Diagram",
        "another task",
        "Task in sec"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成了。两个section、四个任务都按时间线排好了，依赖关系和持续时间也都标注清楚了。您看下整体布局是否符合预期？",
